     1вҶ’# humanize
    12вҶ’This modest package contains various common humanization utilities, like turning a
    13вҶ’number into a fuzzy human-readable duration ("3 minutes ago") or into a human-readable
    14вҶ’size or throughput. It is localized to:
    15вҶ’
    16вҶ’- Arabic
    17вҶ’- Basque
    18вҶ’- Bengali
    19вҶ’- Brazilian Portuguese
    20вҶ’- Catalan
    21вҶ’- Danish
    22вҶ’- Dutch
    23вҶ’- Esperanto
    24вҶ’- European Portuguese
    25вҶ’- Finnish
    26вҶ’- French
    27вҶ’- German
    28вҶ’- Greek
    29вҶ’- Hebrew
    30вҶ’- Indonesian
    31вҶ’- Italian
    32вҶ’- Japanese
    33вҶ’- Klingon
    34вҶ’- Korean
    35вҶ’- Norwegian
    36вҶ’- Persian
    37вҶ’- Polish
    38вҶ’- Russian
    39вҶ’- Simplified Chinese
    40вҶ’- Slovak
    41вҶ’- Slovenian
    42вҶ’- Spanish
    43вҶ’- Swedish
    44вҶ’- Turkish
