    71вҶ’## Usage
    73вҶ’### Integer humanization
    75вҶ’```pycon
    76вҶ’>>> import humanize
    77вҶ’>>> humanize.intcomma(12345)
    78вҶ’'12,345'
    79вҶ’>>> humanize.intword(123455913)
    80вҶ’'123.5 million'
    81вҶ’>>> humanize.intword(12345591313)
    82вҶ’'12.3 billion'
    83вҶ’>>> humanize.apnumber(4)
    84вҶ’'four'
    85вҶ’>>> humanize.apnumber(41)
    86вҶ’'41'
    87вҶ’```
    88вҶ’
